This is your face. On a wall. 
=====================================
Project is hosted at: https://github.com/fahran/facewall

Prequisites:

Intellij IDEA 
Gradle 1.6
JVM 1.7
neo4j 1.9.8 (on Windows, download the .zip version, extract and add the directory to your path.)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To Run:

Start neo4j using "neo4j start"
Deploy the application on a local TomCat server using "gradle tomcatRunWar". It can then be accessed on "localhost:9000/facewall"
Open the project it Intellij, and run "insertFixturesUtility" to populate the database with the test data. 

